WEBVTT

00:00.125 --> 00:02.936
Previously on "Once Upon a Time"...

00:02.961 --> 00:04.994
I remember. Everything.

00:05.297 --> 00:06.663
I love you.

00:07.692 --> 00:08.725
Henry?

00:08.760 --> 00:10.159
You broke the curse.

00:10.195 --> 00:12.762
When I pass the dagger
on to this Guardian,

00:12.797 --> 00:14.497
the Darkness will finally rest.

00:14.532 --> 00:16.165
And I will be reunited with Belle.

00:16.201 --> 00:17.734
Trying to get back to your beloved

00:17.769 --> 00:20.503
has made you the worst version of you.

00:23.975 --> 00:25.341
Hello, Dearie!

00:25.377 --> 00:27.844
Did you really think a
wish realm could hold me?

00:27.879 --> 00:29.712
I need to figure out what my story is.

00:29.748 --> 00:32.115
It's time I figure out where I belong.

00:34.000 --> 00:40.074
